ed="T" n="0718c04"/><persName key="A000992">釋極量</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000048208">中印度</placeName>人也，<name>梵</name>名<persName key="A000992">般剌蜜帝</persName>，此言<persName key="A000992">極<lb
ed="T" n="0718c05"/>量</persName>。懷道觀方，隨緣濟物，展轉遊化，漸達<placeName key="PL000000030464">支<lb
ed="T" n="0718c06"/>那</placeName>，（<placeName key="PL000000048207">印度</placeName>俗呼<placeName key="PL000000030464">廣府</placeName>為<placeName key="PL000000030464">支那</placeName>，名<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">帝京</ref>為<placeName key="PL000000042189">摩訶<anchor xml:id="beg0718003"/>支那<anchor xml:id="end0718003"/></placeName>也）乃於<placeName key="PL000000030435"><placeName>廣州</placeName><placeName>制止<lb
ed="T" n="0718c07"/>道場</placeName></placeName>駐錫。眾知<anchor xml:id="beg0718sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>傳</sic><corr>博</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0718sgsz4"/>達，祈請頗多，<persName key="A000992">量</persName>以利樂<lb
ed="T" n="0718c08"/>為心，因敷祕賾<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g331"/>。</p><p><date key="j19787281978728" when-iso="+0705-06-22"><name>神龍</name>元年乙巳五月二十三<lb
ed="T" n="0718c09"/>日</date>，於《灌頂部》中誦出一品，名《大佛頂如來<lb
ed="T" n="0718c10"/>密因修證了義諸菩薩萬行首楞嚴經》<ptr target="#n92"/>，譯成<lb
ed="T" n="0718c11"/>一部十卷。<placeName key="PL000000049240">烏萇國</placeName>沙門<persName key="A001849">彌伽釋迦</persName>（「釋迦」稍訛，正云「鑠佉」，此曰<lb
ed="T" n="0718c12"/>「雲峯」）譯語，菩薩戒弟子前正議大夫同中書門<lb
ed="T" n="0718c13"/>下平章事<placeName key="PL000000002045">清河</placeName><persName key="A000646">房融</persName>筆受<ptr target="#n3297"/><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>，<placeName key="PL000000031280"><placeName>循州</placeName><placeName>羅浮山</placeName><placeName>南樓<lb
ed="T" n="0718c14"/>寺</placeName></placeName>沙門<persName key="A001896">懷迪</persName>證譯。<persName key="A000992">量</persName>翻傳事畢，會本國王怒<lb
ed="T" n="0718c15"/>其擅出經本，遣人追攝，泛舶西歸。後因南<lb
ed="T" n="0718c16"/>使入<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">京</ref>，經遂流布，有<persName key="A008962">惟慤<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>、<placeName key="PL000000035943">資中</placeName><persName key="A008963">沇<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0718c17"/>各著疏解之。</p>
